00:12:09.800 --> 00:12:12.800 align:middle line:84%
So the gliadin protein
is a direct toxin

00:12:12.800 --> 00:12:14.640 align:middle line:90%
to the gastrointestinal tract.

00:12:14.640 --> 00:12:16.340 align:middle line:90%
It gets partially digested.

00:12:16.340 --> 00:12:18.230 align:middle line:84%
I should point out that
one of the problems

00:12:18.230 --> 00:12:20.300 align:middle line:90%
we have with consuming grains--

00:12:20.300 --> 00:12:24.200 align:middle line:84%
the seeds of grass, as that's
what grains are, literally--

00:12:24.200 --> 00:12:28.910 align:middle line:84%
are they're largely indigestible
because humans are not

00:12:28.910 --> 00:12:31.030 align:middle line:84%
fit to consume the
grasses of the world.

00:12:31.030 --> 00:12:32.780 align:middle line:84%
That's why-- I don't
know if you guys have

00:12:32.780 --> 00:12:34.760 align:middle line:90%
to cut your lawn every summer.

00:12:34.760 --> 00:12:39.140 align:middle line:84%
But I have to have my lawn cut
once a week in the summertime.

00:12:39.140 --> 00:12:40.952 align:middle line:84%
You'd think we could
save the clippings

00:12:40.952 --> 00:12:43.160 align:middle line:84%
and toss it on top of a
salad with a little Roquefort

00:12:43.160 --> 00:12:44.000 align:middle line:90%
dressing.

00:12:44.000 --> 00:12:45.140 align:middle line:90%
But of course, you can't.

00:12:45.140 --> 00:12:46.072 align:middle line:90%
What if you did?

00:12:46.072 --> 00:12:47.280 align:middle line:90%
That's been done, of course--

00:12:47.280 --> 00:12:48.080 align:middle line:90%
people starving.

00:12:48.080 --> 00:12:51.530 align:middle line:84%
People have tried to eat
grasses in their various forms.

00:12:51.530 --> 00:12:53.540 align:middle line:90%
Well, you throw it up.

00:12:53.540 --> 00:12:56.085 align:middle line:84%
It's very painful--
bloating, diarrhea.

00:12:56.085 --> 00:12:58.790 align:middle line:90%
And it comes out undigested.

00:12:58.790 --> 00:13:02.150 align:middle line:84%
And that's because humans
cannot digest grasses--

00:13:02.150 --> 00:13:04.580 align:middle line:84%
nor any of the components
of grasses, whether it's

00:13:04.580 --> 00:13:07.340 align:middle line:90%
the stalk, the husk, the seed.

00:13:07.340 --> 00:13:09.950 align:middle line:84%
So grains are the
seeds of grasses.

00:13:09.950 --> 00:13:13.730 align:middle line:84%
And they are not entirely,
but largely indigestible.

00:13:13.730 --> 00:13:16.190 align:middle line:84%
And that's why so many
of the proteins in grains

00:13:16.190 --> 00:13:19.260 align:middle line:84%
are so toxic to humans,
because we can't digest them.

00:13:19.260 --> 00:13:22.460 align:middle line:84%
So the gliadin protein
is directly toxic.

00:13:22.460 --> 00:13:25.430 align:middle line:84%
It's broken down partially
into small pieces-- peptides.

00:13:25.430 --> 00:13:28.820 align:middle line:84%
Those are also highly toxic to
the gastrointestinal system.

00:13:28.820 --> 00:13:31.010 align:middle line:84%
That wheat germ agglutinin
protein we talked about

00:13:31.010 --> 00:13:33.860 align:middle line:84%
is very toxic to the
gastrointestinal system.

00:13:33.860 --> 00:13:36.500 align:middle line:84%
For instance, it blocks the
hormone cholecystokinin.

00:13:36.500 --> 00:13:38.780 align:middle line:84%
Now, long word but
all it means is,

00:13:38.780 --> 00:13:40.670 align:middle line:90%
I eat something containing fat.

00:13:40.670 --> 00:13:44.120 align:middle line:84%
And the fat provokes my
gastrointestinal tract

00:13:44.120 --> 00:13:46.610 align:middle line:90%
to release this hormone, CCK.

00:13:46.610 --> 00:13:50.290 align:middle line:84%
And that causes your
gallbladder to spit out its bile

00:13:50.290 --> 00:13:52.870 align:middle line:84%
to emulsify fats
and your pancreas

00:13:52.870 --> 00:13:55.910 align:middle line:84%
to release pancreatic enzymes
to break down the fats--

00:13:55.910 --> 00:13:59.060 align:middle line:84%
unless wheat germ agglutinin
is in the vicinity.

00:13:59.060 --> 00:14:02.090 align:middle line:90%
It blocks that path--

00:14:02.090 --> 00:14:04.100 align:middle line:84%
thereby, can't
get your bile out.

00:14:04.100 --> 00:14:07.690 align:middle line:84%
Bile stasis--
gallstones over time.

00:14:07.690 --> 00:14:11.480 align:middle line:84%
Your pancreatic enzymes don't
get expressed like they should.

00:14:11.480 --> 00:14:13.130 align:middle line:84%
And you don't digest
food properly.

00:14:13.130 --> 00:14:14.360 align:middle line:90%
You get acid reflux.

00:14:14.360 --> 00:14:15.680 align:middle line:90%
You get heartburn.

00:14:15.680 --> 00:14:17.900 align:middle line:84%
You get irritable
bowel syndrome.

00:14:17.900 --> 00:14:20.420 align:middle line:84%
Undigested or partially
digested food,

00:14:20.420 --> 00:14:22.340 align:middle line:84%
without enough bile
and pancreatic enzymes,

00:14:22.340 --> 00:14:24.830 align:middle line:84%
rots in your
gastrointestinal tract.

00:14:24.830 --> 00:14:26.240 align:middle line:90%
That has other reactions.

00:14:26.240 --> 00:14:30.390 align:middle line:84%
So you get changes in
bowel flora, dysbiosis.

00:14:30.390 --> 00:14:33.740 align:middle line:84%
There are other reasons that
people consume grains and have

00:14:33.740 --> 00:14:34.550 align:middle line:90%
toxic effects.

00:14:34.550 --> 00:14:36.950 align:middle line:84%
There are numerous
other components,

00:14:36.950 --> 00:14:39.092 align:middle line:84%
like alpha-amylase
inhibitors, and names

00:14:39.092 --> 00:14:40.050 align:middle line:90%
you don't want to know.

00:14:40.050 --> 00:14:42.060 align:middle line:84%
Point being, it's
not just gluten.

00:14:42.060 --> 00:14:42.860 align:middle line:90%
It's not one thing.

00:14:42.860 --> 00:14:44.610 align:middle line:84%
It's really a whole
collection of things.

00:14:44.610 --> 00:14:46.110 align:middle line:84%
And sometimes people
think, oh, he's

00:14:46.110 --> 00:14:47.550 align:middle line:90%
just making it up, exaggerating.

00:14:47.550 --> 00:14:48.350 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:14:48.350 --> 00:14:51.950 align:middle line:84%
It all boils down to the fact
that wheat and related grains

00:14:51.950 --> 00:14:53.930 align:middle line:90%
are the seeds of grasses.

00:14:53.930 --> 00:14:56.870 align:middle line:84%
And Homo sapiens is
just not equipped

00:14:56.870 --> 00:14:59.510 align:middle line:84%
to consume grasses
nor their seeds.

