00:15:48.350 --> 00:15:50.600 align:middle line:84%
They're broken down into
pieces, and sometimes

00:15:50.600 --> 00:15:51.920 align:middle line:90%
not digested at all.

00:15:51.920 --> 00:15:54.350 align:middle line:84%
Like that wheat germ agglutinin
