to small pieces-- about four

00:16:00.230 --> 00:16:03.260 align:middle line:90%
or five amino acids long.

00:16:03.260 --> 00:16:06.380 align:middle line:84%
But those little
proteins or peptides

00:16:06.380 --> 00:16:09.230 align:middle line:84%
have very unique
amino acid structures.

00:16:09.230 --> 00:16:13.090 align:middle line:84%
And that confers an opioid
